'''黑殭菌'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Metarhizium anisopliae''，{{link-en|基名|Basionym}}：''Entomophthora anisopliae''）是一種廣泛分佈於全世界土壤中，且可以在昆虫造成疾病的[[真菌|真菌]]（{{link-en|蟲生真菌|entomopathogenic fungi}}），屬於[[擬寄生物|擬寄生物]]，最早於1879年由俄國微生物學家[[伊利亞·梅契尼可夫|伊利亞·梅契尼可夫]]從{{link-en|奧國賽麗金龜|Anisoplia austriaca}}體內分離<ref name="nmns">{{cite web |author=蕭文鳳 |title=黑殭菌 (Metarhizium anisopliae (Metsch.) Sorokin ) |url=http://digimuse.nmns.edu.tw/da/collections/bf/mt/ex/0b00000181f0da4b/ |work=數位典藏國家型科技計畫 |publisher=[[國立自然科學博物館|國立自然科學博物館]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727092525/http://digimuse.nmns.edu.tw/da/collections/bf/mt/ex/0b00000181f0da4b/ |archive-date=2018-07-27 |access-date=2018-07-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，他以該種金龜的屬名為此真菌的[[種小名|種小名]]。黑殭菌舊時因沒有發現有性世代而被歸屬於[[不完全菌|不完全菌門]]的{{link-en|絲孢菌綱|Hyphomycetes}}<ref name="nmns" />，現在則歸入[[子囊菌門|子囊菌門]]。

過去曾有許多真菌自不同昆蟲身上分離後，經鑑定被歸為本種真菌的[[變種_(植物學)|變種]]<ref name="Driver ''et al.'' 2000">{{Cite journal |last=Driver |first=Felice |last2=Milner |first2=Richard J. |last3=Trueman |first3=John W.H. |date=2000-02 |title=A taxonomic revision of Metarhizium based on a phylogenetic analysis of rDNA sequence data |url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0953756208616378 |journal=Mycological Research |language=en |volume=104 |issue=2 |doi=10.1017/S0953756299001756}}</ref>，但後來經[[核糖體DNA|rDNA]]序列分析後被認為是[[黑殭菌屬|黑殭菌屬]]中的其他獨立物種<ref name="J.F. Bisch., Rehner & Humber (2009)">{{Cite journal |last=Bischoff |first=Joseph F. |last2=Rehner |first2=Stephen A. |last3=Humber |first3=Richard A. |date=2009-07 |title=A multilocus phylogeny of the Metarhizium anisopliae lineage |url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.3852/07-202 |journal=Mycologia |language=en |volume=101 |issue=4 |doi=10.3852/07-202 |issn=0027-5514 |pmid=19623931}}</ref>，例如{{link-en|大孢绿殭菌|Metarhizium majus}}、{{link-en|蝗绿殭菌|Metarhizium acridum}}、{{link-en|贵州绿殭菌|Metarhizium guizhouense}}<ref name="Huang et al. 2005">{{Cite journal |last=Huang |first=B. |last2=Li |first2=C. |last3=Humber |first3=R. A. |last4=Hodge |first4=K. T. |last5=Fan |first5=M. |last6=Li |first6=Z. |date=2005-10-01 |title=Molecular evidence for the taxonomic status of Metarhizium taii and its teleomorph, Cordyceps taii (Hypocreales, Clavicipitaceae). [Erratum: 2006 Apr-June, v. 96, p. 362. |url=http://europepmc.org/article/AGR/IND43805302 |journal=Mycotaxon |volume=94 |issn=0093-4666}}</ref>與{{link-en|棕色绿殭菌|Metarhizium brunneum}}<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Reddy |first=Gadi V.P. |last2=Zhao |first2=Zihua |last3=Humber |first3=Richard A. |date=2014-10 |title=Laboratory and field efficacy of entomopathogenic fungi for the management of the sweetpotato weevil, Cylas formicarius (Coleoptera: Brentidae) |url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022201114001128 |journal=Journal of Invertebrate Pathology |language=en |volume=122 |doi=10.1016/j.jip.2014.07.009}}</ref>等。

==感染過程==
[[File:Ентоцид_(Метаризин).jpg|thumb]]]]
黑殭菌以無性的[[分生孢子|分生孢子]]感染[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]，因分生孢子為綠色，其造成的疾病有時也被稱為{{tsl|en|green muscardine disease|綠殭病}}（{{tsl|en|green muscardine disease}}）。黑殭菌的分生孢子接觸昆蟲的體表後，可以萌發長出[[菌絲|菌絲]]，製造[[酵素|酵素]]分解昆蟲的表皮，並形成[[附著器|附著器]]以穿透昆蟲體壁，進入其體內繼續生長<ref name="gov">{{cite web |author=曾敏南 |date=2005-2 |title=黑殭菌液態量產技術之研發 |url=https://www.coa.gov.tw/ws.php?id=8298 |work=農政與農情 第152期 |publisher=[[行政院農業委員會|行政院農業委員會]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727115148/https://www.coa.gov.tw/ws.php?id=8298 |archive-date=2018-07-27 |accessdate=2018-07-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，當菌絲生長至[[血淋巴|血淋巴]]時會形成游離生長的芽孢體（hyphal bodies），芽孢體可脫離菌絲，如[[酵母菌|酵母菌]]般在血淋巴中自由複製生長，且因其表面有特殊蛋白覆蓋，可遮蔽[[細胞壁|細胞壁]]的[[Β-葡聚糖|Β-1,3-葡聚糖]]等[[病原相關分子模式|病原相關分子模式]]（PAMP），使其不被昆蟲的免疫細胞識別而不受到攻擊<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Wang |first=Chengshu |last2=St. Leger |first2=Raymond J. |date=2006-04-25 |title=A collagenous protective coat enables Metarhizium anisopliae to evade insect immune responses |url=https://pnas.org/doi/full/10.1073/pnas.0601951103 |journal=[[美国国家科学院院刊|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences]] |language=en |volume=103 |issue=17 |doi=10.1073/pnas.0601951103 |issn=0027-8424 |pmc=PMC1458935 |pmid=16614065}}</ref>。黑殭菌的[[菌絲體|菌絲體]]可在昆蟲組織內生長，並生長至昆蟲體外，最終導致昆蟲死亡<ref name="KurttiKeyhani2008">{{Cite journal |last=Kurtti |first=Timothy J. |last2=Keyhani |first2=Nemat O. |date=2008-06-01 |title=Intracellular infection of tick cell lines by the entomopathogenic fungus Metarhizium anisopliae |url=https://www.microbiologyresearch.org/content/journal/micro/10.1099/mic.0.2008/016667-0 |journal=Microbiology |language=en |volume=154 |issue=6 |doi=10.1099/mic.0.2008/016667-0 |issn=1350-0872}}</ref>，被殺死的昆蟲表皮通常會呈紅色。若環境溼度夠高，[[菌絲體|菌絲體]]會從昆蟲屍體上長出，並產生分生孢子而使外觀變成綠色，隨著孢子堆增多也可能轉為灰綠色至黑色<ref name="nmns" />。

許多生活在土壤中的昆蟲都演化出了對抗黑殭菌等{{link-en|蟲生真菌|entomopathogenic fungi}}感染的機制，黑殭菌也演化各種機制加以反制，例如分泌抑制昆蟲免疫細胞的環形[[多肽|多肽]]黑殭菌素（destruxin）<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Pal |first=Subhamoy |last2=St. Leger |first2=Raymond J. |last3=Wu |first3=Louisa P. |date=2007-03 |title=Fungal Peptide Destruxin A Plays a Specific Role in Suppressing the Innate Immune Response in Drosophila melanogaster |url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0021925819834816 |journal=Journal of Biological Chemistry |language=en |volume=282 |issue=12 |doi=10.1074/jbc.M605927200}}</ref>。黑殭菌與昆蟲的[[共演化|共演化]]造成黑殭菌產生大量變種，以分別[[適應|適應]]不同種昆蟲宿主的免疫機制<ref name="Freimoser et al. 2003">{{Cite journal |last=Freimoser |first=F. M. |date=2003-01-01 |title=Expressed sequence tag (EST) analysis of two subspecies of Metarhizium anisopliae reveals a plethora of secreted proteins with potential activity in insect hosts |url=https://www.microbiologyresearch.org/content/journal/micro/10.1099/mic.0.25761-0 |journal=Microbiology |language=en |volume=149 |issue=1 |doi=10.1099/mic.0.25761-0 |issn=1350-0872 |pmid=12576597}}</ref>。

==應用==
黑殭菌與 過去被歸為本種的[[黑殭菌屬|黑殭菌屬]]真菌共可感染超過200種昆蟲<ref name="Cloyd 1999">{{cite journal |author=Cloyd, Raymond A. |year=1999 |title=The Entomopathogenic Fungus Metarhizium anisopliae |url=http://www.entomology.wisc.edu/mbcn/kyf607.html |journal=Midwest Biological Control News |volume=VI |issue=7 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070816080232/http://www.entomology.wisc.edu/mbcn/kyf607.html |archive-date=2007-08-16 |access-date=2007-10-19 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，可用作[[生物農藥|生物農藥]]以控制[[蝗蟲|蝗蟲]]、[[薊馬|薊馬]]、[[白蟻|白蟻]]、[[小菜蛾|小菜蛾]]、[[蟑螂|蟑螂]]、[[金龜子|金龜子]]等害蟲<ref name="gov" />，還可以殺死[[孑孓|孑孓]]，有助控制[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]的傳播<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Bukhari |first=Tullu |last2=Takken |first2=Willem |last3=Koenraadt |first3=Constantianus JM |date=2011-12 |title=Development of Metarhizium anisopliae and Beauveria bassiana formulations for control of malaria mosquito larvae |url=https://parasitesandvectors.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1756-3305-4-23 |journal=Parasites & Vectors |language=en |volume=4 |issue=1 |doi=10.1186/1756-3305-4-23 |issn=1756-3305 |pmc=PMC3051916 |pmid=21342492}}</ref>。黑殭菌不會感染人類與其他脊椎動物，在農業上作為殺蟲劑、殺蟎劑使用相對安全<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Zimmermann |first=Gisbert |date=2007-10 |title=Review on safety of the entomopathogenic fungus Metarhizium anisopliae |url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/09583150701593963 |journal=Biocontrol Science and Technology |language=en |volume=17 |issue=9 |doi=10.1080/09583150701593963 |issn=0958-3157}}</ref>。

[[華盛頓州立大學|華盛頓州立大學]]的研究團隊與[[真菌學|真菌學家]][[保罗·史塔曼兹|保罗·史塔曼兹]]合作，以黑殭菌<ref>{{cite web |title=BeeFriendly™ |url=http://fantasticfungi.com/paul-stamets-bee-friendly/ |publisher=FANTASTIC FUNGI |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205051818/http://fantasticfungi.com/paul-stamets-bee-friendly |archive-date=2017-12-05 |access-date=2018-07-27 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>感染[[蜜蜂|蜜蜂]]的寄生蟲[[瓦蟎|瓦蟎]]，已收到不錯成效，可能有助於解決[[蜂群崩壞症候群|蜂群崩壞症候群]]<ref>{{cite web |date=2017-06-05 |title=Can A Mushroom Save Honey Bees? |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/grrlscientist/2017/06/05/can-a-mushroom-save-honey-bees/#53fcb81e5322 |publisher=[[富比士|富比士]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717171436/https://www.forbes.com/sites/grrlscientist/2017/06/05/can-a-mushroom-save-honey-bees/#53fcb81e5322 |archive-date=2017-07-17 |access-date=2018-07-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

黑殭菌因具有分解昆蟲體壁[[殼聚糖|殼聚糖]]的酵素，可能可用來生產[[生質酒精|生質酒精]]。2017年[[西班牙|西班牙]][[阿利坎特大學|阿利坎特大學]]的一項研究顯示黑殭菌與{{link-en|厚垣普可尼亚菌|Pochonia chlamydosporia}}可以將殼聚糖分解，再經過真菌本身的[[醇脫氫酶|醇脫氫酶]]和{{link-en|丙酮酸脱羧酶|pyruvate decarboxylase}}作用產生[[酒精|酒精]]，有以蝦殼等廚餘生產生質能源的潛力<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Aranda-Martinez |first=Almudena |last2=Naranjo Ortiz |first2=Miguel Ángel |last3=Abihssira García |first3=Isabel Sofía |last4=Zavala-Gonzalez |first4=Ernesto A. |last5=Lopez-Llorca |first5=Luis Vicente |date=2017-11 |title=Ethanol production from chitosan by the nematophagous fungus Pochonia chlamydosporia and the entomopathogenic fungi Metarhizium anisopliae and Beauveria bassiana |url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0944501317302173 |journal=Microbiological Research |language=en |volume=204 |doi=10.1016/j.micres.2017.07.009}}</ref>。

